SCons
will attempt to build packages for each type in the list\&. Example:
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
env\&.Package(PACKAGETYPE=[\*(Aqsrc_zip\*(Aq, \*(Aqsrc_targz\*(Aq], \fI\&.\&.\&.other args\&.\&.\&.\fR)
.fi
.if n \{\
