  env\&.POInit([\*(Aqen\*(Aq, \*(Aqpl\*(Aq]) # messages\&.pot \-\-> [en\&.po, pl\&.po] 
.fi
.if n \{\
.RE
.\}
.sp

\fIExample 2\fR\&. Initialize
en\&.po
and
pl\&.po
from
foo\&.pot:
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
  # \&.\&.\&.
  env\&.POInit([\*(Aqen\*(Aq, \*(Aqpl\*(Aq], [\*(Aqfoo\*(Aq]) # foo\&.pot \-\-> [en\&.po, pl\&.po] 
.fi
.if n \{\
.RE
.\}
.sp

\fIExample 3\fR\&. Initialize
en\&.po
and
pl\&.po
from
foo\&.pot
but using
\fB$POTDOMAIN\fR
construction variable:
