\fBLDMODULEVERSIONFLAGS\fR
.RS 4
Extra flags added to
\fB$LDMODULECOM\fR
when building versioned
\fBLoadableModule\fR\&. These flags are only used when
\fB$LDMODULEVERSION\fR
is set\&.
.RE
